\nThe Restoring Pride will respect the intent of the donor relating to gifts for restricted purposes and those relating to the desire to remain anonymous. With respect to anonymous gifts, the Restoring Pride will restrict information about the donor to only those staff members with a need to know.\r\n\r\nThe Restoring Pride will not compensate, whether through commissions, finders\' fees, or other means, any third party for directing a gift or a donor to the Restoring Pride.'),(59,352,'_give_customize_offline_donations','disabled'),(60,352,'_give_offline_donation_enable_billing_fields_single','disabled'),(61,352,'_give_offline_checkout_notes','In order to make an offline donation we ask that you please follow these instructions::\r\n<ol>\r\n 	<li>Make a cheque payable to \"{sitename}\"</li>\r\n 	<li>On the memo line of the check, please indicate that the donation is for \"{sitename}\"</li>\r\n 	<li>Please mail your check to:</li>\r\n</ol>\r\n{offline_mailing_address}\r\n\r\nAll contributions will be gratefully acknowledged and are tax deductible.'),(62,352,'_give_email_options','global'),(63,352,'_give_email_template','default'),(64,352,'_give_email_logo',''),(65,352,'_give_from_name','Restoring Pride'),(66,352,'_give_from_email','matt.saunders@charitybox.io'),(67,352,'_give_new-donation_notification','global'),(68,352,'_give_new-donation_email_subject','New Donation - #{payment_id}'),(69,352,'_give_new-donation_email_header','New Donation!'),(70,352,'_give_new-donation_email_message','Hi there,\r\n\r\nThis email is to inform you that a new donation has been made on your website: {site_url}.\r\n\r\n<strong>Donor:</strong> {name}\r\n<strong>Donation:</strong> {donation}\r\n<strong>Amount:</strong> {amount}\r\n<strong>Payment Method:</strong> {payment_method}\r\n\r\nThank you,\r\n\r\n{sitename}'),(71,352,'_give_new-donation_email_content_type','text/html'),(72,352,'_give_new-donation_recipient','a:1:{i:0;a:1:{s:5:\"email\";s:27:\"matt.saunders@charitybox.io\";}}'),(73