ington in May of 2019. In this role, his primary responsibilities are to set the direction of the organization, communicate and evangelize the mission and vision of <em>Restoring Pride,</em> and fundraising. Additional responsibilities include communications, finance and Human Resources. Prior to co-founding Restoring Pride, Rob served in a variety of software sales and marketing roles in the data analytics discipline, with a focus on the public sector.&nbsp;</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Robert Dolan, Jr.','','inherit','closed','closed','','54-revision-v1','','','2019-08-10 10:06:18','2019-08-10 09:06:18','',54,'https://restoringpride:8890/54-revision-v1/',0,'revision','',0),(58,1,'2019-08-10 10:06:46','2019-08-10 09:06:46','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chris Wetherington serves as the Executive Director of Restoring Pride, Inc., which he co-founded with Rob Dolan in May of 2019. In this role, his primary responsibility is the day-to-day operations of the organization. Chris spent the past 4 years, until early 2019, on sabbatical traveling across the United States.  During this time, he experienced what it was like to be homeless and he learned first-hand that the systems and services in place are insufficient and overloaded with people requiring help, while providing nothing to those who also identify as LGBTQ. That experience is helping to shape and implement the mission and vision of <em>Restoring Pride</em>.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->','Chris Wetherington','','publish','closed','closed','','chris-wetherington','','','2022-08-02 00:06:46','2022-08-01 23:06:46','',9,'https://restoringpride:8890/?page_id=58',0,'page','',0),(59,1,'2019-08-10 10:06:46','2019-08-10 09:06:46','<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Chris Wetherington serves as the Chief Operating Officer of Restoring Pride, Inc., which he co-founded with Rob Dolan in May of 2019. In this role, his primary responsibility is the day-to-day operations of the organization. Chris spent the past 4 years, until early 2019,